channel.title: [317 Base] Project Purple 317 Client base - 100% GS Stances [Client Base]
channel.description:
[size=5]PLEASE COMMENT (:[/size]
Heres a mostly blank client to build off.
Credits: 30% - The maker of the 317 Cache 70% - Me
-317
[size=18pt]Project Purple![/size]
-Only 16.9 MB (Pretty small for a 317 cache) -100% gs Stances -All overhead prayer icons work -Smite reduces opponents prayer by quarter of hit -moving firecapes -range following - *NOTE* I have not added Customs. (ex Godsdwords, dfs, dfh, etc....) -Blank Client -Working Weapon Specs
--- I have had this for almost 2 years now --- *not my newest work but for beginner coders to have an easy editable 317 client is a good tool to have. *im quitting rsps and i want people to keep this base alive
